indicator.description:
number of studies and projects that have made use of EMIS for baseline information;

Percentage of stakeholders that indicate to be better informed about environmental issues within their area of intervention;

knowledge platform established between key stakeholders at various levels to exchange data on environmental issues;

target.comment:
At the End of Project (2016), 75% of all new projects and studies with an environmental component make use of the EMIS at ANDE;

40% of stakeholders indicate to have been proactively engaged in information exchanges on coastal zone management.

75% of Stakeholders acknowledge the Regional Committee for Sustainable Development (CRDD) within the coastal zone as the main platform for stakeholder information exchange and monitoring of sustainable development in the coastal zone;

